In this tutorial you can learn how to '''build docks''' for ships to load and unload and how to pick a suitable location for a lock. Ships can for instance be used to haul [[en/Manual/Base Set/Cargos/Oil]] from an [[en/Oil rig]] to an [[en/Oil refinery]]. Once you get the hang of building ship routes, you can use ships for other things as well.

